{
  "stem": "24111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "At that time, you must understand, we are talking now '43, October '43, the American and British forces bombed the Reggio Emilia area where we live continuously.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If it was bomb, bombing by day, we knew it is the Americans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If it was bombing by night, we knew it is the British, because they had like a train schedule going.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And not only our area was bombed-- I don't want that you think only we were bombed-- they were bombing, on their way to Germany, overflew us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Train-- trains between Modena and Milan were running, but not on a scheduled basis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "All the passenger cars were taken from Italy and shipped to Germany, because they needed them there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The railways were bombed out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So what they did for-- in Italy, they had either open, open cars, or just, you know, the most true cars available.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they used them for the civilian population.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And when Chichibo traveled, and later on when we traveled, we traveled in open cars or in just cars which were for animals or something like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we didn't know where the train really goes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we didn't know when it will go, but we knew the direction it goes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And this railway goes to-- the next place is Reggio Emilia, and the next place is this and this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And finally, the end of the line is Milano.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we didn't know if it would take one day or two days, or--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now we were-- good that you mention adults, because Jaccia and all the Italians left us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't go into the cloister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only person which stayed with us was Chichibo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, my mother, and you know, but we were the refugees.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
